text:
Rationale:
pytest has powerful fixtures feature. It makes it simplier to write server runner and many other helpers.
Also it alowed to get rid from `_testutil` and `tests`-as-a-package.
It is now possible to run all tests (with as many redis instances as needed).
title: switch from unittest to pytest
